## Ariane Color Tokens

### Semantic Colors (for sentiments)
- \`awake\` - Blue (#0568FD) - Active, primary states
- \`dormant\` - Gray (#6C718C) - Inactive, secondary states
- \`critical\` - Red (#CC3F4D) - Errors, destructive
- \`warning\` - Amber (#AC5F00) - Warnings
- \`success\` - Forest (#15807B) - Success states
- \`featured\` - Lavender (#6B5BEE) - Featured, special

### Text Colors
\`\`\`jsx
<Text color="default.main.primary">    // Black - primary text
<Text color="default.main.secondary">  // Gray - secondary text
<Text color="default.extra.awake">     // Blue - links, active
<Text color="default.extra.critical">  // Red - errors
\`\`\`

