## When to Create Custom Components

Create custom components ONLY when:
1. ❌ No Ariane component serves the purpose
2. ❌ Tailwind overrides cannot achieve the design
3. ✅ User explicitly requests a custom implementation
4. ✅ Building a prototype-specific unique pattern

When creating custom components:
- Use Tailwind CSS classes
- Follow Ariane's color palette and spacing tokens
- Consider if it should be added to Ariane

